The paper discusses the use of VOSviewer for generating journal maps and classifications, which are relevant to several sub-categories in computer science such as digital libraries (cs.DL), information retrieval (cs.IR), social and information networks (cs.SI), software engineering (cs.SD), and computer systems organization (cs.CY). However, since the paper does not focus on any specific sub-category, these are only likely possibilities and not definitive.
